{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"testFail"},{"kind":"text","text":"()"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function can be called multiple times from the same test."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can use this function if your test failed in a recoverable way.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Do not use this function if the failure of a test could cause","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other tests to malfunction."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Calling this function will not stop the test from running, you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"need to return from the test function yourself. So you can"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"produce additional diagnostic messages or even continue running"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the test.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If not called from inside a test, this function does nothing."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that unlike [func"},{"code":"GLib.test_skip","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] and [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.test_incomplete"},{"type":"text","text":"],"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this function does not log a message alongside the test failure.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If details of the test failure are available, either log them with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.test_message","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] before [func"},{"code":"GLib.test_fail","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"], or use"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.test_fail_printf"},{"type":"text","text":"] instead."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/testFail()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"title":"testFail()","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"symbolKind":"func","roleHeading":"Function","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"testFail","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"()","kind":"text"}],"externalID":"s:4GLib8testFailyyF","role":"symbol"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/testfail()"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Indicates that a test failed.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/testFail()":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/testfail()","title":"testFail()","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/testFail()","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"testFail","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"()","kind":"text"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Indicates that a test failed."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","title":"GLib","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib","abstract":[]}}}